Privacy Policy for AI Weather App Last updated: 4-21-25
Thank you for using AI Weather App. Your privacy is important to us.
Data Collection
AI Weather App does not collect, store, or share any personal data from users. We do not request or process location data, personal identifiers, or usage analytics.
Third-Party Services
Our app utilizes Gemini Nano for AI-powered weather reports. While Gemini Nano operates within the app, AI Weather App itself does not collect or transmit any user data to third parties.
User Consent
Since AI Weather App does not collect any user data, no explicit consent is required.
Security
As we do not store or handle user data, no additional security measures are required beyond standard app safeguards.
User Rights & Data Retention
AI Weather App does not store any user information; therefore, there is no data to access, modify, or delete.
